Subject: [PATCH] python3-maxminddb: add new package (backported from upstream)

---
 lang/python/python3-maxminddb/Makefile | 42 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 42 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 lang/python/python3-maxminddb/Makefile

diff --git a/lang/python/python3-maxminddb/Makefile b/lang/python/python3-maxminddb/Makefile
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..00d3340
--- /dev/null
+++ b/lang/python/python3-maxminddb/Makefile
@@ -0,0 +1,42 @@
+#
